***SWIPE👈🏻***
I have never understood the popularity of @TonyRobbins, a man who has always been so clearly a misogynistic, greedy, self-serving charlatan. This is a man who has trashed the #MeToo movement and all of the women who spoke out about being victims of sexual abuse, has bullied woman after woman, and has claimed that “emotional abuse” is just a term that women use to describe things that men have said to them that they didn’t like (see last two slides). If you’re a fan of this guy, you’re being played. You need to wake up and stop putting money in his pocket. There are high-quality, compassionate, educated, intelligent, benevolent motivational speakers out there, and Tony Robbins ISN’T ONE OF THEM! 🙅🏼‍♀️

Why was it hurtful? Why was it harmful? How does what you say promote interpersonal violence, racism, sexism, classism? What have you learned - how has your mind expanded? Credit the people who have helped you better understand. And then teach what you have learned.

Without any of these, he sucks and is some false, self-aggrandizing profit that  scams people out of an enormous amount of money, under the guise of helping people. This is a whole new level. I hope we can find out more of this. Most importantly - I hope he does some introspection and shuts the fuck up long enough to humble himself, learn to say “I was wrong” or “I need to learn about this,” and apologize. And change. It’s obviously fucking eye roll that while he is talking about how people need to take responsibility and accountability for their life - he completely lacks the ability to take a look at himself.  This was absolutely disgusting. I hope people share more. I am sure there is much more. This is really bad. And I think that if he actually ACTUALLY became teachable, malleable, all these things he claims he is - the situation would end up being good for humanity. He is powerful and his scope is huge. Imagine if he was evolved enough to keep evolving.
